===Articles===
* Siaw-Fong Chung 锺晓芳, Chu-Ren Huang 黄居仁: Using collocations to establish the source domains of conceptual metaphors. Journal of Chinese Linguistics, Vol. 38.2 (2010).
* Stephen R. Bokenkamp: Chinese Metaphor again: Reading-And Understanding-Imagery in the Chinese Poetic Tradition. Journal of the American Oriental Society , Vol. 109, No. 2 (1989): 211-221 [[@http://www.jstor.org/stable/604426|JSTOR]] 
* Alfreda Murck: Degrees of Clarity and Obscurity in Chinese Images. Extrême-Orient Extrême-Occident, Vol. 30 (2008): 45-66 [[http://extremeorient.revues.org/94|Link]] 
