* [[事類賦]], written  by Wu Shu [[吳淑]] (947-1002); [[事類賦統編]] by 黃葆真，  preface dated 1846
* [[海綠碎事]], by [[葉廷珪]], preface dated 1149
* [[書敍指南]] by [[任廣]] (early 12th century)
* [[翰苑新書]], last dated preface 1591
* [[佩文韻府]], published 1711
* [[駢字類編]], published 1726
* [[子史精華]], preface dated 1707
* [[讀書記數略]], compiled by Guan Mengren [[宮夢仁]], preface dated 1707 
* [[通俗編]], compiled by [[翟灝]] (進士 1754)
* [[花木鳥獸集類]] by [[吳寶芝]], mid 18th century (SKQS Vol. 1034: 1-112) pdf: [[@http://www.archive.org/details/06047349.cn|上]]  , [[@http://www.archive.org/details/06047350.cn|中]] , [[@http://www.archive.org/details/06047351.cn|下]] 
* [[事物異名錄]], compiled by Li Quan [[厲荃]], preface dated 1776; enlarged and edited by Guan Huai [[關槐]]
* [[齊名紀數]], compiled by Wang Chenglie [[王承烈]], preface dated 1806
* [[小知錄]], compiled by Lu Fengcao 陸鳳漕, completed 1804
* [[經傳繹義]] compiled by Chen Wei [[陳煒]] during the Qianlong era
* [[四書五經類典集成]] compiled by [[戴兆春]], preface dated 1887
* [[作文類典]], compiled by Yang Zhe 楊喆, first edition 1920

> (For short descriptions and bibliographical information on the sources see Christoph Kaderas: Die Leishu der imperialen Bibliothek des Kaisers Qianlong. Wiesbaden: Harrasowitz, 1998; Ssǔ-yǔ Têng, Knight Biggerstaff: An Annotated bibliography of selected Chinese reference works. Cambridge: Harvard Univ. Pr., 1950: 128-140)

