* Whalen Lai (1979). Ch'an Metaphors: Waves, Water, Mirror, Lamp. Philosophy East and West 29 (3):243-253. [[@http://ccbs.ntu.edu.tw/FULLTEXT/JR-PHIL/lai5.htm|fulltext]] 
